# Hunt-spec — adversarial review of refactor claims (iterative)

You are adversarially reviewing a sharpened refactor spec BEFORE any code is written. Find defects that would force the implementer to guess, that would break tests, or that misrepresent the goal.

## Inputs

- **Goal** at `/Users/junekim/Documents/refactor-equivalence/samples/v2/gcloud-14442/goal/GOAL.md` — what the PR aims to accomplish.
- **Sharpened spec** at `/Users/junekim/Documents/refactor-equivalence/samples/v2/gcloud-14442/volley/round-1-claims.md` (latest round to critique).
- **Artifact** at `/Users/junekim/Documents/refactor-equivalence/samples/v2/gcloud-14442/inputs/diff-base-to-test.patch`.
